high_descs: Turn right and head towards the counter space in between the sink and stove.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Take several steps to the left and find the left cabinet above the stove.
Open the cabinet and place the spoon in the glass cup.
Take out the cup from the cabinet.
Turn right towards the sink.
Place the cup with the spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a spoon in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go toward the dishwasher, then turn left to face the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the spoon on the counter, to the right of the stove.
Turn around, then go to face the stove, then look up at the cabinet above the stove, on the left.
Put the spoon in the cup, in the cabinet.
Take the cup from the cabinet.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards the sink, then turn slightly left and face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the spoon on the counter that is right of the stove top and left of the fork.
Holding the spoon, move slightly to the left to stand in front of the stove top on the left hand side.
Open the leftmost cabinet above the stove top and put the spoon into the glass that is left of the salt shaker.
Take out the glass and spoon (still inside the glass) from the cabinet and shut the cabinet.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the glass with the spoon in it into the right hand sink over the top of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a spoon inside of it into the sink.
